rows.name:
As a Driver scout, I do worry about the
welfare of our young recruits!

rows.label: tlk45320121_03_msg0002
rows.name:
There was a lad who enrolled just
the other day, in fact.

rows.label: tlk45320121_03_msg0003
rows.name: Elnoth, I think his name was.

rows.label: tlk45320121_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Said he wanted to become a Driver
to help out his siblings. That's some
passion for you!

rows.label: tlk45320121_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I hope life's treating him well in
Superbia...
